events.title: Night Tempo
events.location: Seattle, Washington, United States Of America
events.description: The Neptune Theatre is located in Seattle, Washington at 1313 NE 45th Street in Seattle's University District. This is a general admission event. The ADA section on the seating map does not represent a specific seat location. There is an 8 ticket limit for this event. Accounts found in violation of the posted ticket limit may be cancelled without notice. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. Unless otherwise noted, each person must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. Mobile ticket delivery will be delayed until 4 days prior to event.
